{"tid":2046841,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學界黃店告急] 中學手足請入！","createTime":"2020-06-01T16:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T17:34:55.000Z","uid":312513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8be7d8b669f6af3f891e44cf6648ea5996091b","tid":2046841,"uid":312513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"嗱 我求你唔好屌我係打手住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知好多中學手足想補習 但又唔想補藍燈塔 古代教育嗰啲大型垃圾補習社<br />\n日校老師藍定黃就話無得揀啫<br />\n但補習社藍黃就一定有得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以小弟想同各位介紹返間黃到金嘅蚊型良心補習社<br />\n有幾黃？唔講啦 自己睇下咪知黃唔黃囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Av5O1qw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAv5O1qw.jpg&h=9c5f0b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecp8gYV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fecp8gYV.jpg&h=2699dac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzWnmqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzWnmqC.jpg&h=c65fefb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W6mRZcj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW6mRZcj.jpg&h=ac38f9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班老師真係好有心去教書<br />\n所以見到佢哋收生收得咁辛苦真係心痛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你睇到依度 依家你可以屌我係打手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都希望可以喺到鼓勵大家喺唔同生活層面都可以積極啲幫襯黃店<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9bd88cb69f13f179478338fca8bdc888e2ab29","tid":2046841,"uid":219339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51724bc4a784d55394af8b7f3039a7a0e23a3a67","tid":2046841,"uid":312513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;推唔郁啊嗚"},{"pid":"0715aeab859df29c9d90f1a56cdeacd03a1944d3","tid":2046841,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:24:53.000Z","msg":"但好多人補撐警june leung間野"},{"pid":"99d078fcba267ee56a61172bbed527d749c116b9","tid":2046841,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:29:40.000Z","msg":"雖然要錢生活  不過好多群都義補緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0204b45b0140ee769f9568dbca179afedc4b28ca","tid":2046841,"uid":312513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0715aeab859df29c9d90f1a56cdeacd03a1944d3","tid":2046841,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:24:53.000Z","msg":"但好多人補撐警june leung間野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:31:21.000Z","msg":"其實有好多黃補習社同老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多中學手足都唔肯郁下手指上網搵下<br />\n一個二個湧曬去所謂有名氣嘅大補習社"},{"pid":"8c6e85cc2c16aab99151812f313bd9dcdaea6f65","tid":2046841,"uid":312513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d078fcba267ee56a61172bbed527d749c116b9","tid":2046841,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T17:29:40.000Z","msg":"雖然要錢生活  不過好多群都義補緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB